frequency, and to highlight the importance of surface geometry in coil design.\n  Conclusion: Like the Principle of Reciprocity from which it is derived, the\nOptimality Principle offers both a conceptual and a computational shortcut. In\naddition to providing quantitative targets for coil design, the Optimality\nPrinciple affords direct physical insight into the fundamental determinants of\ncoil performance.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 6 Aug 2018 19:49:05 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-08-08"}
