es to a\nsmall static solution, stable in the entire exterior of a schwarzschild cone\nwith positive mass, which then is patchable to the interior results.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 7 Aug 2018 15:19:18 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-08-08"}
